{"tid":1631537,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"海牙法庭 與 羅馬規約","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:10:22.000Z","uid":291779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"125b2642de9f5fb83013f76649860b64f4511a0a","tid":1631537,"uid":291779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"一直都好多人講開要求<strong>海牙法庭</strong>介入，調查政府和警察有冇濫用警權或使用酷刑<br />\n<br />\n咁海牙法庭可以點樣介入呢？就要根據羅馬規約 <a href=\"http://legal.un.org/icc/statute/chinese/rome_statute(c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegal.un.org%2Ficc%2Fstatute%2Fchinese%2Frome_statute%28c&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=bf49c1eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://legal.un.org/icc/statute/chinese/rome_statute(c</a>).pdf 俾國際法庭的權力<br />\n想睇繁體中文既話呢到有個 Google Translate 版 <a href=\"https://filebin.net/edsvi76r6wllyth1/rome_statute_traditional_chinese.pdf?t=28d0wcq5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffilebin.net%2Fedsvi76r6wllyth1%2Frome_statute_traditional_chinese.pdf%3Ft%3D28d0wcq5&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=0def0485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://filebin.net/edsvi76r6wllyth1/rome_statute_traditional_chinese.pdf?t=28d0wcq5</a><br />\n<br />\n羅馬規約 第12條： 法庭既權力可以用於 <br />\n1. 在締約國境內發生既事<br />\n2. 被告人國藉係<strong>締約國國藉</strong><br />\n咁中國唔係締約國，所以檢查官係不能對HK Police 檢控的<br />\n除非被告人係例如英藉指揮官，因為英國係締約國<br />\n<br />\n呢個只係我暫時理解，有D野希望大家幫手做<br />\n1. 希望有多D人可以幫手諗下有冇其他野可以叫海牙法庭做<br />\n2. 又或者有冇D咩人係締約國國藉的？<br />\n<br />\nReference： <br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/29084/黑警-與羅馬規約\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F29084%2F%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-%E8%88%87%E7%BE%85%E9%A6%AC%E8%A6%8F%E7%B4%84&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=753ac3a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/29084/黑警-與羅馬規約</a>"},{"pid":"c4d12c3b813811dfe708e1ed1eea91a019cf450d","tid":1631537,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c65b2c68130ccb10a797594fcb2f64909fc93461","tid":1631537,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99729f2354c824a4ab82db10a3bc966f5e3fecd2","tid":1631537,"uid":258409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"起碼可以郁隻講yellow object件white object先，chinazi唔係締約國預料中事"},{"pid":"3f823c0fb22c14fedb11c1f3f9d5e840ed7e8d9f","tid":1631537,"uid":291779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99729f2354c824a4ab82db10a3bc966f5e3